data.description: Come see this beautiful corner lot, 3 bedroom, 2 and a half bath, with an upstairs bonus room and exterior added on screened-in patio. HVAC installed last year, and the roof is approximately 5 years old. Privacy wood fence out back and a small above ground pool to enjoy throughout the summer. Vinyl flooring throughout the main area, and carpeted bedrooms, stairs, and upper level. $60 annual HOA covers the community entry point and community events/activities. This home has a lot of character and is move-in ready for the whole family to enjoy. All appliances and storage sheds included. Sold as-is.
